OL,3,CAppointment of watchdog 'start of real
OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,FA charity that supports people with
OL,7,Fautism has welcomed the appointment of
OL,8,Fan independent watchdog to oversee the
OL,9,Froll out of Northern Ireland's Autism
OL,10,FStrategy.
OL,12,FEma Cubitt, a qualified solicitor who
OL,13,Fhas provided voluntary support for
OL,14,Findividuals and families struggling to
OL,15,Faccess care and support, has been
OL,16,Fselected for the role of Autism
OL,17,FReviewer.
