OL,3,CAppointment of watchdog 'start of real
OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,FKerry Boyd, CEO of Autism NI heralded
OL,7,Fthe appointment as the "start of real
OL,8,Fchange" for Northern Ireland's autism
OL,9,Fcommunity.
OL,11,FMs Boyd said: "Now that we have a
OL,12,Freviewer appointed, she needs to be
OL,13,Flooking at the overall services
OL,14,Fprovided to autism families and
OL,15,Fautistic people throughout Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
