OL,3,CAppointment of watchdog 'start of real
OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,F"And look at things like, no matter
OL,7,Fwhere you live, it shouldn't depend on
OL,8,Fwhere you live and how quickly you can
OL,9,Faccess services and what the waiting
OL,10,Flists look like.
OL,12,F"And also get onto the ground and
OL,13,Fspeak to autistic people themselves
OL,14,Fand find out what are the issues that
OL,15,Fthey are finding.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
