OL,3,CAppointment of watchdog 'start of real
OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,F"Autism NI receives over 11,000 calls
OL,7,Fevery single year and we know that
OL,8,Fthere is great difficulties accessing
OL,9,Fservices still and we need to see that
OL,10,Fchange and I feel that this role is
OL,11,Fwhat is needed to ensure that that
OL,12,Fhappens".
OL,14,FEma Cubitt was selected for the role
OL,15,Ffollowing a public selection process
OL,16,Fand will take up the post for five
OL,17,Fyears from September.
