OL,6,FShe is a Law and Governance graduate
OL,7,Ffrom Ulster University and holds a
OL,8,Fpostgraduate Diploma in Legal Studies
OL,9,Ffrom Queen's University.
OL,11,FMrs. Cubitt said: "I am honoured to
OL,12,Ftake on this responsibility and I am
OL,13,Fcommitted to serving the autistic
OL,14,Fcommunity.
