OL,3,CAppointment of watchdog 'start of real
OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,F"It is crucially important that we all
OL,7,Fwork together across our public
OL,8,Fservices to address the challenges
OL,9,Ffaced by autistic people and I am
OL,10,Fcommitted to ensuring that their
OL,11,Fvoices, and those of their families
OL,12,Fand carers, are heard.
OL,14,F"Alongside Northern Ireland's autistic
OL,15,Fcommunity, I am dedicated to
OL,16,Foverseeing consistent delivery of high
OL,17,Fstandards and best practice across
OL,18,Fgovernment departments and public
OL,19,Fservices."
