OL,6,FAlthough Mrs Cubitt has been appointed
OL,7,Fby the Department of Health, the role
OL,8,Fis independent.
OL,10,FHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt said: "I
OL,11,Funderstand the importance of this post
OL,12,Ffor autistic people and their
OL,13,Ffamilies. I would like to wish Ema the
OL,14,Fvery best as she prepares to take up
OL,15,Fthe position.
