OL,4,Cchange' for autism community in NI
OL,6,F"We all have a responsibility and a
OL,7,Frole to play in ensuring that autistic
OL,8,Fpeople and their families can feel
OL,9,Funderstood, accepted and supported
OL,10,Fwithin our communities and in the
OL,11,Fdelivery of our services.
OL,13,F"My department will continue to work
OL,14,Fin partnership across government
OL,15,Fdepartments, the health and social
OL,16,Fcare sector, public bodies and the
OL,17,Fcommunity and voluntary sector, to
OL,18,Fmake this happen."
